casebody.data:
E.F., a Minor, By and Through His Parents, Eric FULSANG, et ux., et al., petitioners,
v.
NEWPORT MESA UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT. No. 16-1533. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 2, 2017.

*170On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Endrew F. v. Douglas County School Dist. RE-1, 580 U.S. ----, 137 S.Ct. 988, 197 L.Ed.2d 335 (2017).
